data.description: In the heart of Midtown just a few blocks from Capital Complex, Midtown Cinema, Riverfront Park and so much more! This is a 2 bedroom 1 1/2 bath home with a full basement along with NEWER Heat Pump / Central Air and a New roof! Take a look and add your personal touches to modernize this gem. A nice sized kitchen with a penusila set up featuring plenty of countertop space and an eat in area to host. All appliances will convey. Kitchen features ceramic tile flooring. The family room is a great space to gather around which has plush carpet. Upstairs hosts both bedrooms. The owner's bedroom features a massive walk in closet with tons of space and a private bath. The 2nd bedroom also has a walk in closet too. The 2nd floor has a convenient laundry room. The basement could be finished at ease as it stays dry and can easily be finished for another living room/rec space or home office. Enjoy your evenings on your covered patio area which is a great spot to enjoy the privacy outdoors as it's fully enclosed. Plus a small fenced in portion. Added convenience of rear parking with 1 assigned parking space along with overflow community parking.
